data.meta_description: Son of Virginia natives William H Brown and Mary Vasseur Brown.  Married to Margaret Parthenia Hooker on July 25, 1855 in Orange County, North Carolina.  Henry and Margaret were the parents of: LeClair H Brown  Claudius Wright Brown Anne Vasseur Brown  Julia Estelle Brown Henry Nicholas Brown  Margaret Brown Gay ...
